---
title: Conditions & Actions
description: How TealTiger policies express conditions and produce actions.
---

> **Version:** v1.1.0  
> This page documents behavior guaranteed in TealTiger v1.1.0.


# Conditions & Actions

## Conditions

Describe when a policy triggers (e.g., tool name is disallowed, PII detected, budget exceeded).

## Actions (DecisionAction)

- ALLOW
- DENY
- REDACT
- TRANSFORM
- REQUIRE_APPROVAL
- DEGRADE

## Example (illustrative)

```json
{
  "tools": {
    "file_delete": {"allowed": false}
  }
}
```
